sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Calendar Manage Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component

    User->>UI: Open calendar manage page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW-->>UI: Render management cards (classes, activities, institute holidays, public holidays)

    User->>UI: Click one management card
    UI-->>UI: Navigate to selected calendar management page
